 started signing large clients ebm what are your priorities for the year ahead benoit fouilland so for  we remain focused on a clear set of priorities first innovate on the core product and expand our core business worldwide second scale criteo sponsored product across markets and integrate it with the criteo technology third deploy criteo predictive search in the us in france and in additional key markets fourth build and leverage our pooled assets like our user graph our universal catalog and sales attribution for brands across retailer partners all of that in order to benefit our ecosystem and fifth develop test launch compelling new products such as prospecting app installs offline crm data onboarding and video ebm so all in all another great quarter for you… benoit fouilland yes im pleased with our strong performance in q delivering sustained profitable growth and cash flow we execute on our plans and we see exciting avenues of growth for  and beyond ebm benoit fouilland criteos cfo thanks for being with us benoit fouilland thank you contactname first name last name email emailsubjectsubjectmessagemessageopt in send me the ceodirect video qa interviews send me the weekly newsletter news you can usephonethis field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged this iframe contains the logic required to handle ajax powered gravity forms we use cookies to ensure that we give you the best experience on our website if you continue to use this site we will assume that you are happy with itokread more criteo q  results  benoît fouilland  eurobusiness media menu contactfr writing storytelling digital benchmarking graphic design training media training presentation coaching financial presentations crisis communication video ceodirect™ interviews corporate videos motion design events panel moderating  mc speech writing consulting  scripting webcasting team clients news  views menucontactfr q  resultsbenoît fouillandcfoparis may   – criteo a global performance ma